    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed and all achieved levels met or exceeded required levels for Model Risk Level 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not assessed on the basis that the assessment team judged it inapplicable given direct correspondence between validation and COU input conditions. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
